            text: "Users get practical next steps while support and R&D can see where assistance works, fails, or needs stronger rules.",
          },
          {
            label: "Legacy System Meaning",
            text: "It wraps legacy CMMS expertise in guided tools that make existing configuration logic easier to use and improve.",
          },
        ],
        tags: [
          "Engineering Assistant",
          "CMMS Reasoning",
          "Guided Troubleshooting",
          "Support Tooling",
