        buildLabel: "Built the trust layer around listings",
        built:
          "Connects school-email access, listing states, signed media, inquiry threads, reports, admin review, email privacy, cache refresh, and cron jobs.",
        valueLabel: "Makes the marketplace feel real",
        rdValue:
          "The case study shows the operations and safety details that sit behind a simple student listing experience.",
        fields: [
          {
            label: "Problem",
            text: "A marketplace looks simple until trust, identity, privacy, moderation, media, notifications, and cleanup need to work together.",
